                    "goto": "gather",
                    "text": "Sure thing!"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "gather",
            "text": "You'll need a few pine boards, some wood glue, and a 16 oz claw hammer. I'll supply what you lack and show you how to check for square corners.",
